Prometheus Metrics (Port 9090):
  - http_request_duration_seconds
  - http_requests_total
  - process_cpu_seconds_total
  - process_memory_bytes
  - federated_learning_training_loss
  - federated_learning_workers_active

Grafana Dashboards (Port 3000):
  Credentials: admin/admin
  
  Available Dashboards:
  1. System Overview
  2. API Performance
  3. Federated Learning Status
  4. Resource Utilization
  5. Error Rate Analysis
  6. Model Training Progress
  7. Worker Health Dashboard

Loki Log Aggregation (Port 3100):
  Log Sources:
  - Frontend access logs
  - Backend application logs
  - Database query logs
  - FL coordinator logs
  - Worker node logs

Log Queries:
  Frontend logs: {service="frontend"}
  Backend logs: {service="backend"}
  Database logs: {service="mongo"}
  FL logs: {service="federated-learning"}

Viewing Logs:
  View all services:
    docker-compose logs -f
  
  View specific service:
    docker-compose logs -f backend
  
  View last 100 lines:
    docker-compose logs --tail=100 backend
  
  Follow with timestamps:
    docker-compose logs -f --timestamps backend
  
  Export to file:
    docker-compose logs > logs.txt
